title: AI and Machine Learning for Official Statistics - AIML4OS
text: AI and Machine Learning for Official Statistics (AIML4OS) is an ESSnet project aimed at delivering a comprehensive suite of resources, guidelines, methodologies and use cases for the implementation of AI/ML in Official Statistics. There are 15 funded countries in the consortium. The project is running from April 2024 to March 2028.
